messages.messageBody:
wow, you miss a couple of days on this list and you are sooo out of the
loop! I've been reading and catching up. I admire you guys (gals) that
can read and respond and know what's going on! I read the article in
People. Not nearly enough info about Ren and her family, but I liked
what I read. I do wish I had some unschoolers near me though, b/c I get
lonely sometimes too... been shunned a couple of times but nothing
major. I would love to come to a conference but they are all too far
(we are in Alabama). Maybe one day I'll make it. And I can't believe
the controversy over the blog about homosexuals. A 4-H group really got
upset over that?!?! WOW! Lot's going on... Lots of reading to do.
Forgive me if I don't post much. I love reading what everyone else is
saying and it helps me! Thanks for the list and the help!
Leslie
